p: To predict possible antigenic properties and the three-dimensional (3D) structure of SHNP (Seoul virus BjHD01, Accession Number AY627049.2) using bioinformatic tools, the entire sequence of SHNP (NCBI ID: AAT45728.1) was downloaded from the NCBI website ( www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/protein) and used for analyses.
